Elara Lace â€“ Minimalist Lingerie Homepage

Elara Lace is a refined and minimalist e-commerce homepage designed to showcase a luxury lingerie brand through clean UI, strong typography, and soft visual storytelling.
This project was built as part of a personal portfolio to demonstrate front-end development skills, HTML/CSS structure, component styling, and custom branding integration.

The result is a fast, elegant, and responsive landing page that mirrors the sophistication and femininity of the brand.

